sg":"講漏左 知道人地無影相之後仲要無道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:02:20.000Z","msg":"你講返事實出嚟緊係冇問題<br />\n大家都係理性嘅溝通為主<br />\n邊洗驚俾人話係鬼<br />\n至於冇講sorry嘅話你咪代佢地講返sorry<br />\n大家都係兄弟 要無私啲為大家付出"},{"pid":"5bfc64a47c004e5b4fde17dea35a615902336ec6","tid":1418411,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"你識條鐵我地偉大既前線，我代表勇武宣佈樓主係三毛"},{"pid":"f7ce1ccaa9339db4ca570fc51f9a7a74c0c831f8","tid":1418411,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2644fb6a5ab9029cb0c07a714a29f53f877f78a2","tid":1418411,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:08:03.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"920b9bc9427006fa4a1fb034950200afa1179397","tid":1418411,"uid":10860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bfc64a47c004e5b4fde17dea35a615902336ec6","tid":1418411,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"你識條鐵我地偉大既前線，我代表勇武宣佈樓主係三毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S845cbC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS845cbC.png&h=8f7655b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分化完未呀？？<br />\n我上咗好多年高登/連登<br />\n不斷屈毛呢種手段係五毛最愛<br />\n亂咁屈人毛令人分唔清五毛<br />\n你今日瘋狂出post分化係想勇武發脾氣唔搞？"},{"pid":"644aebf1331c1e11970dd0785072ae910d83162a","tid":1418411,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:17:44.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ff4eb8290c3532856961a3fd4cd7cc4399a5775d","tid":1418411,"uid":79047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c0faa8562ada7fbb6fb15ed0d6719fb618fd676","tid":1418411,"uid":10860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89f611e1d1b95fa0c5f4f9d3b72b3faff6e586ef","